CRP2A Calibration Curve

Canberra Inspector 1000 - LaBr #1

CRP2A Luminescence Team

2020-05-21

Source: vignettes/crp2a_1.Rmd
crp2a_1.Rmd
library(gamma)
library(magrittr)

Import Files

# Import CNF files for calibration
spc_dir <- system.file("extdata/BDX_LaBr_1/calibration", package = "gamma")
(spc <- read(spc_dir))
#> A collection of 7 gamma spectra: BRIQUE, C341, C347, GOU, LMP, MAZ, PEP

# Import CNF files for background noise measurement
bkg_dir <- system.file("extdata/BDX_LaBr_1/background", package = "gamma")
(bkg <- read(bkg_dir))
#> Gamma spectrum:
#> *  name: BDF
#> *  date: 2009-07-24 10:22:46
#> *  live_time: 18296.71
#> *  real_time: 18327.16
#> *  chanels: 1024
#> *  energy_min: -1.92
#> *  energy_max: 3323.47
